==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Bourdon
<hw>Bour"don`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. See
<er>Burden</er> a refrain.]</ety> <fld>(Mus.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>A
drone bass, as in a bagpipe, or a hurdy-gurdy. See <er>Burden</er> (of a
song.)</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>A kind of organ stop.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

